# Tooltip

## Anatomy

- trigger
- bubble
- arrow

## States

- hidden
- visible
- delayed
- hover
- focus

## Variants

- top
- right
- bottom
- left
- rich tooltip

## Tokens

- `--color-foreground`
- `--color-background`
- `--space-*`
- `--radius-sm`
- `--shadow-md`
- `--duration-quick`

## Accessibility

- Tooltip content is supplementary, not required to complete a task.
- Trigger references tooltip with `aria-describedby`.
- Tooltip appears on keyboard focus as well as hover.
- Escape hides when open.
